{"title":"提升Powershell使用体验","date":"2019-07-17T00:00:00.000Z","link":"windows/oh-my-posh","tags":["Fluent Terminal","oh-my-posh","powershell"],"updated":"2022-04-27T15:24:01.763Z","content":"<h1 id=\"终端terminal推荐\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"windows/oh-my-posh#终端terminal推荐\"></a> 终端（Terminal）推荐<a href=\"windows/oh-my-posh#终端terminal推荐\"></a></h1>\n<h2 id=\"windows-terminal\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"windows/oh-my-posh#windows-terminal\"></a> Windows Terminal<a href=\"windows/oh-my-posh#windows-terminal\"></a></h2>\n<p>GitHub地址：<a href=\"https://github.com/microsoft/terminal\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">https://github.com/microsoft/terminal</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li>主题推荐 GitHub地址：<a href=\"https://github.com/mbadolato/iTerm2-Color-Schemes/tree/master/windowsterminal\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">https://github.com/mbadolato/iTerm2-Color-Schemes/tree/master/windowsterminal</a></li>\n<li>笔者自己配的主题：<a href=\"https://github.com/HanyuuLu/toolbox/tree/master/poshTheme\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">https://github.com/HanyuuLu/toolbox/tree/master/poshTheme</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"fluent-terminal\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"windows/oh-my-posh#fluent-terminal\"></a> Fluent Terminal<a href=\"windows/oh-my-posh#fluent-terminal\"></a></h2>\n<p>GitHub地址：<a href=\"https://github.com/felixse/FluentTerminal\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">https://github.com/felixse/FluentTerminal</a></p>\n<h2 id=\"cmder\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"windows/oh-my-posh#cmder\"></a> Cmder<a href=\"windows/oh-my-posh#cmder\"></a></h2>\n<p>GitHub地址：<a href=\"https://github.com/cmderdev/cmder\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">https://github.com/cmderdev/cmder</a></p>\n<h1 id=\"powershell-美化\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"windows/oh-my-posh#powershell-美化\"></a> PowerShell 美化<a href=\"windows/oh-my-posh#powershell-美化\"></a></h1>\n<h2 id=\"oh-my-posh\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"windows/oh-my-posh#oh-my-posh\"></a> oh-my-posh<a href=\"windows/oh-my-posh#oh-my-posh\"></a></h2>\n<h3 id=\"安装\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"windows/oh-my-posh#安装\"></a> 安装<a href=\"windows/oh-my-posh#安装\"></a></h3>\n<ul>\n<li>若您从未更改过powershell的执行权限（或者不知道此物为何物），则需要更改powershell的执行权限以运行脚本</li>\n<li>需要管理员权限</li>\n</ul>\n<figure class=\"highlight\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"built_in\">Set-ExecutionPolicy</span> Bypass</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n<ul>\n<li>安装posh-git</li>\n</ul>\n<figure class=\"highlight\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">Install-Module posh-git -Scope CurrentUser</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n<ul>\n<li>安装oh-my-posh本体</li>\n</ul>\n<figure class=\"highlight\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">Install-Module oh-my-posh -Scope CurrentUser</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n<h3 id=\"启用\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"windows/oh-my-posh#启用\"></a> 启用<a href=\"windows/oh-my-posh#启用\"></a></h3>\n<h4 id=\"手动启动\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"windows/oh-my-posh#手动启动\"></a> 手动启动<a href=\"windows/oh-my-posh#手动启动\"></a></h4>\n<figure class=\"highlight\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"built_in\">Import-Module</span> oh-my-posh    <span class=\"comment\"># 导入模块</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">Set-Theme Paradox   <span class=\"comment\"># 使用Paradox主题</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n<h4 id=\"伴随powershell自启\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"windows/oh-my-posh#伴随powershell自启\"></a> 伴随powershell自启<a href=\"windows/oh-my-posh#伴随powershell自启\"></a></h4>\n<p>如果<span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math><semantics><mrow><mi>p</mi><mi>r</mi><mi>o</mi><mi>f</mi><mi>i</mi><mi>l</mi><mi>e</mi><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">指</mi><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">向</mi><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">的</mi><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">文</mi><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">件</mi><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">存</mi><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">在</mi><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">，</mi><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">则</mi><mi>p</mi><mi>o</mi><mi>w</mi><mi>e</mi><mi>r</mi><mi>s</mi><mi>h</mi><mi>e</mi><mi>l</mi><mi>l</mi><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">启</mi><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">动</mi><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">时</mi><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">会</mi><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">顺</mi><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">带</mi><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">启</mi><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">动</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">profile指向的文件存在，则powershell启动时会顺带启动</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.8888799999999999em;vertical-align:-0.19444em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathdefault\">p</span><span class=\"mord mathdefault\" style=\"margin-right:0.02778em;\">r</span><span class=\"mord mathdefault\">o</span><span class=\"mord mathdefault\" style=\"margin-right:0.10764em;\">f</span><span class=\"mord mathdefault\">i</span><span class=\"mord mathdefault\" style=\"margin-right:0.01968em;\">l</span><span class=\"mord mathdefault\">e</span><span class=\"mord cjk_fallback\">指</span><span class=\"mord cjk_fallback\">向</span><span class=\"mord cjk_fallback\">的</span><span class=\"mord cjk_fallback\">文</span><span class=\"mord cjk_fallback\">件</span><span class=\"mord cjk_fallback\">存</span><span class=\"mord cjk_fallback\">在</span><span class=\"mord cjk_fallback\">，</span><span class=\"mord cjk_fallback\">则</span><span class=\"mord mathdefault\">p</span><span class=\"mord mathdefault\">o</span><span class=\"mord mathdefault\" style=\"margin-right:0.02691em;\">w</span><span class=\"mord mathdefault\">e</span><span class=\"mord mathdefault\" style=\"margin-right:0.02778em;\">r</span><span class=\"mord mathdefault\">s</span><span class=\"mord mathdefault\">h</span><span class=\"mord mathdefault\">e</span><span class=\"mord mathdefault\" style=\"margin-right:0.01968em;\">l</span><span class=\"mord mathdefault\" style=\"margin-right:0.01968em;\">l</span><span class=\"mord cjk_fallback\">启</span><span class=\"mord cjk_fallback\">动</span><span class=\"mord cjk_fallback\">时</span><span class=\"mord cjk_fallback\">会</span><span class=\"mord cjk_fallback\">顺</span><span class=\"mord cjk_fallback\">带</span><span class=\"mord cjk_fallback\">启</span><span class=\"mord cjk_fallback\">动</span></span></span></span>profile指向的脚本，所以我们将上述语句写入该文件中</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"built_in\">New-Item</span> <span class=\"variable\">$PROFILE</span> -Type File    <span class=\"comment\"># 创建文件，若提示文件已存在则可以直接编辑文件</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"string\">\"Import-Module oh-my-posh    # 导入模块\"</span> &gt;&gt; <span class=\"variable\">$PROFILE</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"string\">\"Set-Theme Paradox   # 使用Paradox主题\"</span> &gt;&gt; <span class=\"variable\">$PROFILE</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n<h1 id=\"字体更换\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"windows/oh-my-posh#字体更换\"></a> 字体更换<a href=\"windows/oh-my-posh#字体更换\"></a></h1>\n<h2 id=\"更纱黑体\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"windows/oh-my-posh#更纱黑体\"></a> 更纱黑体<a href=\"windows/oh-my-posh#更纱黑体\"></a></h2>\n<p>常规字体是没有办法完全显示oh-my-posh的powerline字符的，因此我们需要一种好看的powerline字符</p>\n<ul>\n<li>笔者在此安利Sarasa Gothic / 更纱黑体 / 更紗黑體 / 更紗ゴシック<br>\n微软应用商店<a href=\"https://www.microsoft.com/store/productId/9MW0M424NCZ7\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">下载</a><br>\nGithub Release<a href=\"https://github.com/be5invis/Sarasa-Gothic/releases\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">下载</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"字体更换简介\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"windows/oh-my-posh#字体更换简介\"></a> 字体更换简介<a href=\"windows/oh-my-posh#字体更换简介\"></a></h2>\n<p>建议在以下位置更换使用 Sarasa Term SC 字体（Term为终端字体，SC为简体中文，其他简写请参考应用商店或github readme说明）</p>\n<ul>\n<li>cmd</li>\n<li>powershell</li>\n<li>Fluent Terminal</li>\n<li>Windows Terminal</li>\n<li>vsCode （编辑器和内置终端）</li>\n<li>Visual Studio</li>\n<li>其他可能使用到终端或者编辑代码的位置</li>\n</ul>\n","prev":{"title":"非标准数据简单网格化的一种方法","link":"Others/positionMesher"},"next":{"title":"简单的k-means实践","link":"Others/k-means"},"plink":"ilucia.github.io/windows/oh-my-posh/","toc":[{"title":"<a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\"></a> 终端（Terminal）推荐","id":"终端terminal推荐","index":"1","children":[{"title":"<a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\"></a> Windows Terminal","id":"windows-terminal","index":"1.1"},{"title":"<a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\"></a> Fluent Terminal","id":"fluent-terminal","index":"1.2"},{"title":"<a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\"></a> Cmder","id":"cmder","index":"1.3"}]},{"title":"<a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\"></a> PowerShell 美化","id":"powershell-美化","index":"2","children":[{"title":"<a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\"></a> oh-my-posh","id":"oh-my-posh","index":"2.1","children":[{"title":"<a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\"></a> 安装","id":"安装","index":"2.1.1"},{"title":"<a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\"></a> 启用","id":"启用","index":"2.1.2"}]}]},{"title":"<a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\"></a> 字体更换","id":"字体更换","index":"3","children":[{"title":"<a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\"></a> 更纱黑体","id":"更纱黑体","index":"3.1"},{"title":"<a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\"></a> 字体更换简介","id":"字体更换简介","index":"3.2"}]}],"copyright":{"author":"Ilucia Niu","license":"<a rel=\"license\" href=\"http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/\">知识共享署名 4.0 国际许可协议</a>","published":"2019年7月17日","updated":"2022年4月27日"}}